data.name: btnAddCountries.ToolTip
data.value:
Add selected delegates to the committee.
Delegates must be selected in the "Available delegates" list.
Added delegates are given voting rights by default; use the small arrows to move added delegates to the correct list.

data.name: ToolStripDropDownButton2.ToolTipText
data.value:
Load / save speaking list
Provides the ability to save and reload a speaking list. For example, if a speaking list is open on a draft resolution when an amendent is introduced, requiring a new speaking list, you can save the resolution list and reload it later when discussion on the amendment is finished.
